The paper deals with the problem of constructing coresets for the fuzzy $K$-means problem, which is a clustering problem. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also discusses approximation algorithms and streaming algorithms, which are topics commonly studied in the categories cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.DB (Databases).
